Subject: [PATCH 219/793] media: i2c: adv7511: Add DT binding to this driver

TRD is using this driver with this binding.
hdmio@39 {
	 compatible = "adv7511";
	 reg = <0x39>;
	 ..
};

This DT support was removed by commit:
"Merge tag 'v3.12' into master-next"
(sha1: cd30bed1eb9cddb9bd24c0fcd13bdbba6373ac1f)

